---
// Pull quote — Margaret Mead, centered, between Bio and Work.
---
<aside class="pullquote" aria-label="Pull quote">
  <div class="container">
    <hr class="rule-red" aria-hidden="true" />
    <blockquote>
      Never doubt that a small group of thoughtful, committed citizens can change the world; indeed, it&rsquo;s the only thing that ever has.
    </blockquote>
    <p class="attribution">Margaret Mead</p>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .pullquote {
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem) 0;
  }
  .pullquote .container { text-align: center; }
  .pullquote .rule-red { margin: 0 auto 1.75rem; }
  .pullquote blockquote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.2vw, 2.5rem);
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: var(--lw-slate);
    max-width: 30ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .attribution {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: var(--fs-eyebrow);
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--lw-muted);
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
  }
</style>
